casebody.data:
Friday, May 15, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

97-1173. Keefe v. Youngstown Diocese of the Catholic Church.

Stark App. No. 1996CA00265. On May 1, 1998, appellant filed a list of additional authorities. Appellant’s document contains more than the list of citations to additional authorities permitted by S.CtPrac.R. IX(7), and therefore is not in compliance with S.Ct.Prac.R. IX(7). Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that appellant’s list of additional authorities be, and hereby is, stricken.
